name: Fallguytalk(Unofficial)
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: fall guy
des:
Ever wanted to talk with a fall guy? Then this is a perfect skill.

You can tell him that you won, that you lost and even how depressed you are after getting eleminated 1,000 times in a row!!!
It also talks with you in any situation, good or bad!

For now this skill is still in it's early days and theres is not much to do but in the future i will add many new features, like (More) playing game music, win counter and more!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
